213
00:17:52,687 --> 00:17:54,727
<font color="#ffff00"><b>We won't leave until you get here.</b></font>

214
00:17:55,087 --> 00:17:57,167
<font color="#ffff00"><b>And if you don't arrive soon,</b></font>

215
00:17:57,767 --> 00:17:59,247
<font color="#ffff00"><b>we can't be friends anymore.</b></font>

216
00:18:01,567 --> 00:18:03,847
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Because Shancai will kill us all.</b></font>

217
00:18:05,927 --> 00:18:08,687
<font color="#ffff00"><b>We will all be dead.
