218
00:18:26,207 --> 00:18:27,607
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Is that good enough?</b></font>

219
00:18:40,087 --> 00:18:40,927
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Xiaoyou.</b></font>

220
00:18:41,487 --> 00:18:42,407
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It'll be all right.</b></font>

221
