<font color="#ffff00"><b>Please.</b></font>

222
00:19:33,007 --> 00:19:34,327
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Thank you for the lesson.</b></font>

223
00:19:35,927 --> 00:19:37,887
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'll practice it when I get home.</b></font>

224
00:19:40,767 --> 00:19:42,007
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Ximen.</b></font>

225
00:19:44,327 --> 00:19:46,167
<font color="#ffff00"><b>When we last saw each other,</b></font>

226
00:19:46,687 --> 00:19:48,087
<font color="#ffff00"><b>you were still in high school.</b></font>

227
00:19:48,687 --> 00:19:50,047
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You're all grown up now.</b></font>

228
00:19:50,567 --> 00:19:51,687
<font color="#ffff00"><b>How have you been?</b></font>

229
00:19:55,487 --> 00:19:56,847
